org.spongepowered.api.entity.living

Interface Living

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataHolder, DataSerializable, Entity, Identifiable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Aerial, Ageable, Agent, Ambient, Animal, Aquatic, ArmorStand, Bat, Blaze, Boss, CaveSpider, Chicken, ComplexLiving, Cow, Creeper, EnderDragon, Enderman, Endermite, Ghast, Giant, Golem, Guardian, Horse, Human, IronGolem, MagmaCube, Monster, Mooshroom, Ocelot, Pig, Player, Rabbit, Sheep, Silverfish, Skeleton, Slime, SnowGolem, Spider, Squid, Villager, Witch, Wither, Wolf, Zombie, ZombiePigman

    public interface Living
extends Entity
    Represents an entity that is living, and therefor can be damaged.

    Living entities can have PotionEffects, breathing air under water, custom names, and become invisible.
